---
title: Chipotle Chicken Breast Strip Wraps  with Tomato Salad and Chips
description: This Chipotle Chicken Breast Strip Wraps is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
